iten by Lexander and dictated by StinkyFeetLover26<br>\r\nThis is the tale of Michael; a simple college student thrust into an unparalleled situation. Though facing such a new world view Michael tries to take advantage of his new world. However, he may end up regretting his ambition.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlex's Fate --- Written by StinkyFeetLover21 and dictated by Lexander<br>\r\nThis is the story of Alex, a tiny caught up in the world of being small...very small!  How will he cope with this situation?  Only time will tell!</span></div></div>",
