        "brief_description":"A Co-op Story Project about a shrunken man mostly focused on feet.",
        "created":1609557960,
        "description":"<td align=\"left\" class=\"norm\">This is a project to create two stories written by one author and directed by the other one. How this works is each author will write a chapter. Then the other author will write the choices for that author's interactive story. Thus allowing each author to make completely free decisions in the other author's story and then get to read what unfolds based on their choices.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nYou as a reader just get to enjoy two stories that will eventually be branching interactive stories as time goes on and each of us authors keeps adding to them. Hope you Enjoy what the stories eventually become.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTags: Feet<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span class=\"clred\"><b>This Project is Privite!</b></span> Any Additions to this Story Will Be Removed<br>\r\nHowever, if you would join in on this Co-op writing project we are open to allow more Co-op writing stories in the project.<br>\r\nAny are welcome to join our discord and talk with us about joining the project.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMain Authors: <span class=\"noselect\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\" oncontextmenu=\"uport_ajax_rt_opts (event, this, 'leightonx7', '', '', '', '10', '', 'ON', '101205266'); hide_uport (); this.shown=1; return false;\" onclick=\"uport_ajax_opts (event, this, 'leightonx7', '', '', '', '10', '', 'ON'); hide_uport (); this.shown=1;\"><a title=\"Username: leightonx7\r\nMember Since: March 3rd, 2016\r\nClick for links!\" style=\"line-height: 1em;font-size:1em;font-weight:bold;cursor:pointer;\">Lexander</a></span> <span class=\"noPrint\">(<a title=\"View leightonx7's Community Recognition\" class=\"blue2roll\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"javascript:LaunchPop('https://www.Writing.Com/main/authors/action/overall/user_id/leightonx7',%20'CommunityR_101205266',%20'400',%20'650')\">21</a>)</span> <a class=\"imgLink imgPortLink\" onmousedown=\"if(event.which == 3) { event.preventDefault(); var mywin = window.open('https://www.Writing.Com/main/portfolio/view/leightonx7','